      <h1>Hi, I'm Alaric!</h1>
      <p>Who are you?</p>
      <p style="clear: both"></p>
    </header>

    <div id="content">

    <p>
      Welcome to my vanity domain.
    </p>

    <p>
      For a living, I work
      for <a href="http://www.rainstor.com/">RainStor</a>. In my spare
      time, I'm the Cub Scout Leader
      for <a href="http://www.cranham-scouts.org.uk/">Cranham</a>, and
      I pursue <a href="http://www.kitten-technologies.co.uk/">my own
      open source software projects</a>, experiment with metalwork and
      electronics, and learn things (I'm
      studying <a href="http://www.lojban.org/">Lojban</a>
      and <a href="http://krav-maga.com/">Krav Maga</a>, and anything
      else interesting I read on the Internet or pick up a book
      on). My goal in life is to develop technology, to make
      everything more awesome. If you bumped into me in the street,
      the first thing you'd probably notice is the amount of
      technology I'm wearing.
    </p>

    
