      My Amazon wishlist contains <a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/exec/obidos/wishlist/2R5MPFM6TL0DE/ref=wl_em_to">A tiny subset of the things I want</a>; or you can send me some <a href="http://www.bitcoin.org/">Bitcoin</a> to <a href="bitcoin:1ALAricQjEj5ErpDCLDZWYHGv15jMq1gEM">1ALAricQjEj5ErpDCLDZWYHGv15jMq1gEM</a>.
